{"tid":941781,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［選項故］Engine女神育成記","createTime":"2018-12-15T06:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T15:59:48.000Z","uid":106965,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d832b96b2ab64b496d100363ca53fd7b8856602","tid":941781,"uid":106965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"我係一個好平凡嘅女仔，靚又稱唔上，又唔係豬西肥婆，但係入到engine毒L科，好平凡嘅女仔都會變得好唔平凡。<br />\n<br />\n至於我點解會想揀engine? 中學果時數學唔差，成績又唔係特別好，咁就好自然會碌左入水泡科engine啦。<br />\n<br />\n終於等到去大學嘅reg day，面對住唔多攤位嘅推銷，我同兩個男仔中同，都一齊報左engine嘅ocamp。<br />\n<br />\n講下兩個男仔，一個叫啊日，一個叫啊進。兩個都係我同班同學。<br />\n<br />\n啊日個人就幾靚仔，同我幾熟，會同我傾心事，但佢有個一齊左幾個月嘅女朋友，喺dse後表白成功。<br />\n<br />\n啊進就係典型engine仔，唔識打扮，有時個頭油到好似幾日冇洗頭，但佢為左reg day特登去左剪髮gel頭。原本其實都只係我同啊日嚟，係見佢苦苦哀求我地先俾佢跟埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啊日彈結他好叻，去到興趣學會就諗住報音樂學會嘅ocamp，仲話想搵一班人係大學搞busking。<br />\n啊進就入大學想食囡囡，去左報最多女既天文學會，佢又話，聽討論區嘅人講，天文soc嘅ocamp係最好玩。<br />\n<br />\n你決定報咩學會嘅ocamp？<br />\nA. 音樂學會<br />\nB. 天文學會<br />\nC. 佛教學會<br />\nD. 唔報"},{"pid":"7d122dba31e04971fc4f58110b77b3aed88fd62a","tid":941781,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"rejupas"},{"pid":"1e57630434f781483b2a36671e559815d63e8844","tid":941781,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d122dba31e04971fc4f58110b77b3aed88fd62a","tid":941781,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"rejupas"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"入禾含"},{"pid":"309e2e80afbb026f38641b621815810646bf1734","tid":941781,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"D"},{"pid":"6eb3daf44bdddc7550d9bf80eef386f344a2ec3e","tid":941781,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"D"},{"pid":"b782acded82edeb83077b2e03a7e8c06835efc12","tid":941781,"uid":225371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:13:14.000Z","msg":"識揀一定揀D"},{"pid":"e82e706dbcae40de4800e21595ee08afa208a791","tid":941781,"uid":106965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e57630434f781483b2a36671e559815d63e8844","tid":941781,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d122dba31e04971fc4f58110b77b3aed88fd62a","tid":941781,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"rejupas"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"入禾含"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"又含大會變重甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7fcb8510024a76a52732b5a808ea83c9eb5833","tid":941781,"uid":52221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"c55a46fe928472e02ae3c810cd65f58534a4394d","tid":941781,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"屌你，我係阿進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23a56fd39952c33c50cbc54fc56c62eec3bb807","tid":941781,"uid":106965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"哇$250玩2日1夜有冇貴左啲啊...<br />\n對於唔係特別有錢嘅我，雖然啊日慫恿我去陪佢去音樂學會ocamp，但我都係決定唔去，況且頭先個姐姐都話9月開左學仲可以報名，咁遲啲再決定都得。<br />\n<br />\n去到hall果一條街，hall嘅人好似一堆餓狼搶食物咁不斷招攬freshman去佢地hall參觀。而啊日都想行一行男hall，因為佢女朋友唔俾佢住男女hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢就去左男hall嘅攤位。<br />\n<br />\n啊進突然見到有間hall啲囡囡好正，就拉左我去果間hall嘅攤位睇。果間係一間男女hall，男女同層果隻，係我仲睇緊間hall係咩嚟果時，佢已經走左入去諗住去行hall tour。有個女仔見我同啊進傾計，但隻腳又企左係度唔入去，就講：<br />\n去行一行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔會㩒住你唔俾你走，又有紀念品拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟埋個fd行啦。<br />\n<br />\n你嘅決定係：<br />\nA. 去<br />\nB. 唔去<br />\nC. 去搵啊日，同佢一齊行男hall"},{"pid":"a55f6fe557177710921e04cd4495c061d8a55774","tid":941781,"uid":108758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:36:21.000Z","msg":"a"},{"pid":"9f3f19d5417e1f7fb3fc721752a2ac1627bb8d86","tid":941781,"uid":225371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"92823ec3ad6f076c793d5df235378889d491edc4","tid":941781,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"C"}]}